FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782568081
OL,3,CAirshow expected to attract 'more
OL,4,Cvisitors' than ever before
OL,6,FFarnborough Airshow CEO, Gareth
OL,7,FRogers, told ITV Meridian it will
OL,8,Fprovide a multi-million pound boost to
OL,9,Fthe local economy.
OL,11,F"For weeks and weeks and weeks there
OL,12,Fis people in hotels, eating at
OL,13,Frestaurants, going in shops, buying
OL,14,Ftheir petrol, buying their newspapers,
OL,15,Fdrinks etcetera.
OL,17,F"It's a massive deal for the local
OL,18,Fcommunity. Millions of pounds of
OL,19,Feconomic benefit, but also a fabulous
OL,20,Fflying display for them to watch as
OL,21,Fwell at the end.''
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782568081
OL,3,CAirshow expected to attract 'more
OL,4,Cvisitors' than ever before
OL,6,FFour thousand workers are currently on
OL,7,Fsite building the infrastructure
OL,8,Fneeded to host the show.
OL,10,FOver 60 different British aircraft
OL,11,Ffeatured in the Farnborough Airshow,
OL,12,Fwhen it first opened its doors to the
OL,13,Fpublic in 1948.
OL,15,FThis year it will run from Monday,
OL,16,FJuly 20 to Friday, July 24, with
OL,17,Fdisplays from more than 100 civil and
OL,18,Fmilitary aircraft.
OL,20,FMr Rogers added: "We are expecting
OL,21,Fmore visitors from around the world.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
