OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782568081
OL,3,CAirshow expected to attract 'more
OL,4,Cvisitors' than ever before
OL,6,F"There is so much happening on a geo-
OL,7,Fpolitical situation. There is so much
OL,8,Fhappening in a new technology
OL,9,Fsituation and those things are
OL,10,Fcolliding and coming together.
OL,12,F"We are expecting some really great
OL,13,Facts."
OL,15,FHis optimism was shared by Dudley
OL,16,FSharland, a local Bed and Breakfast
OL,17,Fowner, who is hoping for a
OL,18,F"significant upturn in business".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
